      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne ¶ 26. Dec. 1881. ¶ T. Wilson Esqr &amp;c, ¶ Undersecretary. ¶ Sir...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">81.12.26</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Thomas Wilson</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">V81/11657 unit<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont"
                    style="font-weight: bold; background-color: #FFFF00; ">get number</seg>, VPRS 3991/P inward registered correspondence, VA 475 Chief Secretary's Department, Public Record Office, Victoria.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style=""/>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; ">NOTE: this letter is amongst<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     </seg>
                     <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont"
                          style="font-weight: bold; background-color: #FFFF00; ">1883</seg>
                     <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; ">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>letters, with the letter [82.01.17] where M informed Wilson that Sonder had died</seg>
                  </p>
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; ">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     </seg>
                     <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; color: #C00000; ">I am not sure that it is necessary to report on the context of the fgiling of this letter if the location details are completed</seg>.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                  </p>
               </note>Melbourne</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">26. Dec. 1881.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">T. Wilson Esqr &amp;c,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Undersecretary.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have the honor to solicit a interview with the honorable J. M. Grant, the Chief Secretary, as I am anxious to explain to the honorable Gentleman my desire, to acquire for this Government a large collection of dried plants, formed since the last 50 years by a leading botanist of Europe,<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>i.e. W. Sonder.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>the collection having been offered to me in preference to any other purchaser, as I have been in communication with the owner since 36 years. The price is fixed at about £850, and about £50 would additionally be required for the transit. This addition to our own collection, which for Australian species is by far the largest anywhere, would render our botanic museum, in reference to dried plants, one of the largest in the world.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>M to T. Wilson, 17 January 1882<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>(<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #0017FB; ">in this edition as 82-01-17a</seg>)<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #1527FF; ">reported Sonder's death, and further pressed for the purchase.</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #1527FF; ">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>See Short (1990).</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I have the honor to be,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sir,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>your obedient servant</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
         </div>
